"sdf">notes</a></u> that shareholders would probably prefer =E2=80=9Can une=
lected emperor=E2=80=9D to =E2=80=9Ca squabbling committee.=E2=80=9D I supp=
ose it also helps that Fox=E2=80=99s stock is
up 24% year to date.<br/><br/>This is life imitating art imitating life, of=
 course. As one media exec texted me, <b>Jesse Armstrong</b>, the creator o=
f HBO=E2=80=99s <i>Succession</i>, probably would have rejected this plotli=
