ast temporarily reneged on his commitment to participate in the ABC News de=
bate on September 10. In a somewhat batshit crazy statement, Trump comms ch=
ief <b>Steven Cheung </b>said it would be =E2=80=9Cinappropriate=E2=80=9D t=
o schedule a debate with <b>Kamala Harris</b> because some Democrats think =
Harris is =E2=80=9Ca Marxist fraud who cannot beat President Trump, and the=
y are still holding out for someone=E2=80=99s =E2=80=98better.=E2=80=99=E2=
=80=9D Obviously, that=E2=80=99s quite a dodge on Trump=E2=80=99s part. In =
any event, ABC News is in a holding pattern until Harris formally secures t=
